11. Nodes are automatically cleaned up when they go out of scope due to smart pointers
12. Returns a snapshot containing the before/after cache statistics

The `CacheProbeNode` class implements the required `valueChanged` method with a simple call to the base class implementation. The function returns a `CacheStatsSnapshot` structure containing the relevant cache statistics for testing purposes.

